## Decrypt the Password

Copy the encrypted password from the email and save it to a file, then decrypt it:

```bash
# Save the encrypted content to a file (paste the email content)
cat > encrypted-password.txt << 'EOF'
[encrypted content from email]
EOF

# Decrypt using your GPG key
gpg --decrypt encrypted-password.txt
```

When prompted, enter your GPG passphrase.

The output will show your decrypted password.

